title: Izibiliboco
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Western, South African, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. A small, cozy eatery decorated with plants and ar. It's run by a vegetarian South African woman who also creates unique jewelry which is on display in the restaurant. Most dishes are vegetarian with meat as add-on by demand. Jazzy music played in the background to accompany your meal.
